  {
   "question": "What are the highest-consensus Restoration Shaman items in Phase 3?",
   "answer": "Totem of Healing Rains (93%), Cataclysm Chestguard (74%), Girdle of Fallen Stars (71%). When an item sits above ~70% among top parsers, treat it as the priority drop to chase."
  },
  {
   "question": "Should I follow this list exactly for Phase 3?",
